5
One Move Captures Black (8)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to Play.\b0
\par It is a very easy problem. If it were a real game, however, both players might have been mistaken, considering black's group to be alive.
\par
\par It is a kind of a blind spot.
\par One move leaves black helpless.
\par
\par }
