Diagram 1 (Misreading)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White 1 is a mistake in reading that you might easily make in a real game.
\par
\par Black thrusts between whites stones with 2 and then plays dansu at 4 to guarantee life - this might be how both players read the situation here.
\par
\par However, this is nonsense.
\par }
