Diagram 2 (Unenthusiastic)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}{\f1\fmodern\fprq2\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par What is white 1 about?
\par It is completely unenthusiastic.
\par
\par \pard\nowidctlpar\qj Black can live with 2. Anyone can see that. Instead of W1, if white plays at \b\f1 A\b0\f0 , black plays \b\f1 B\b0\f0  so this does not work either. If white plays at \b\f1 B\b0\f0 , black answers at \b\f1 C\b0\f0 , so this too does not work.
\par }
